Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:19.70,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(733,390)\fad(450,0)}各自的前程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂不斷輪回
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反復轉世凡塵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反復身纏悲嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲嘆於天國為上帝所擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是美好的真諦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的靈魂卻從真諦的圈子中脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往更高處邁出了腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後之子的遺骸 不在此地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就宣告著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不對未知的來世抱有憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Altair也絕不會滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼好畏懼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後之子告訴了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是活在奇跡之中的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖言惑眾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕後的Altair已然是日薄西山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此 Iron C的輸出功率也變得不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠詭辯來欺瞞民眾亦不是長久之計
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未影 你竟敢大放厥詞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的潛入行動可謂帶來了極大的福音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這家伙 讓Jin就這麼犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為Altair作出了巨大的貢獻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是值得他以性命相換的貢獻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對RareIgler的巢穴所造成的打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與眾真實的夏娃候補的接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且太陽之翼的轉世之身也終於要亮相了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin的靈魂如果得知自己取得的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必要高興得顫抖不已了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 說不定之後會轉生為神聖Altair的最初之子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你真正的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定不會原諒我和Altair的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================提供=================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來前往Neo Stanley的墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}校船在2點到達 注意時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己關在房間裡不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直消失著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想就這樣一直關著自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白她的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也失去了重要的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃·鈴白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動總司令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人總覺得好難應付
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把柚葉·蘇爾從房間裡帶出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行…現在我想讓她靜一靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在以合體這種聯繫他人的行為為義務的這所學園裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不允許有人獨善其身 陷入孤獨的深淵之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說獨善其身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎 柚葉的Element能力是消失的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她因失去了Jin·無雙而導致力量失控
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼而毀滅自身也不足為奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉 我能進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想你多少吃點什麼會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用勉強的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就放在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉的氣息變得好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin曾經對我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我跟他一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我如果回應了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 漸漸變弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要 我不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想和Jin道別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道別的話不說也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對Jin也好 對柚葉也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡柚葉 珍視柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:06:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在Jin過去所棲息的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家終於開始意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己身處生死攸關的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須感謝死去的伙伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你把人的性命當成什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想輟學回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的覺悟就只有這種程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是為了保護這顆星球而被選出來的Element啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們居然忘記了這份榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mix 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣叫人不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都承受了嚴苛的訓練而努力至今
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪 難道你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在學校 連我們都不在怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會被置之不顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被吸入到那巨大的洞裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我落入別人挖的洞裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕難從命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪·W·霍爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖洞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有…居然有這麼多洞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖這麼多洞要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Altair界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin·無雙來自名為Altair的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進而 從他遺留下來的數據中判明了Altair的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們企圖擄走女性Element
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後與Altair的戰鬥應該會愈發激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必會使埋葬在這裡的死者變得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了應對這場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你們也埋在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓穴特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================CM========================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要在這剛埋掉同伴的墓地裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋本身就已經很不願意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是被埋在墓穴裡 我表示最強烈的拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 這果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太惡劣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家明明都已經傷心欲絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所說的活簡直不可理喻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們被生所束縛著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過與死者同眠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們對生的渴望將顯著增強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜念 邪念 哀念 執念 怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切的觀念將奪走你們靈魂的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且在與死亡比鄰的戰場上化作枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們必須在這裡死一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說死一次?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓對生的執著一度爆發出來並將之割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短暫的死亡其盡頭究竟有著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你們的眼睛好好確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經算是一個行將就木的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為不久後的死做一次演習也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想陪在他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想陪在Jin的身邊 哪怕只是一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼深的洞 只能靠我自身來填滿它了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要填上這麼辛苦挖出來的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是要命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那看穿一切的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑 什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼安靜啊 周圍一片死寂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還是有聲音的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在土壤上爬行的蟲子的動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總在蠕動著挖道前行的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人不快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一群蛆蟲從氣孔中鑽了進來似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體就這樣風化變脆 土崩瓦解似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疙疙瘩瘩的 就像在逐漸腐化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸腐化 隨後回歸塵土的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin與我 能合而為一嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 要回歸塵土了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 就回不了地面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕 這個洞是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總司令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說這也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這群罪孽深重的無翅正在深沉的黑暗中苦苦掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想與他們一同享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到冥界旅行的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 被埋沒吧 神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋沒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是亂來 也不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這是安迪挖的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所挖的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這麼想就不害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連我的絕望預知也看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那個時候我會看得見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果御子乃真的是希爾菲轉世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 你是不會被御子乃選中的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有被選中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她留了下來 我真覺得生不如死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許死了也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有Jin的世界 這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉的氣息在逐漸消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔的飛翔之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑西卡的扭轉之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特的聲音 怪炎的絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有柚葉的消失之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自的思念在激蕩 如此下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易變得這麼要好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易覺得大家能夠心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次回到這裡來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生的話 又會被遺棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 再也不想被別人遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在被遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瑪塔 在被遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 再也不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要再被遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在這裡 像這樣和Jin在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤苦伶仃地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃·鈴白 這就是你所持有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人僅僅終結了生命這並不是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同頭發與牙齒脫落一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體的細胞 意識 心靈都在一刻緊接一刻地死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刻緊接一刻地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一旦拘泥於已逝的古舊的自己並固步自封
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們就會從巨大的宇宙洪流中被分割出來 四散飄零
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃·鈴白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量就是將那些四散飄零的人再次維繫起來的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維繫的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將禁錮已逝的古舊自己的屍骸為食糧茁壯生長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像蘑菇的菌絲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在肉眼所看不見的大地深處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生與死的夾縫間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將變得離散飄零的靈魂逐漸團結在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一萬兩千年前開始就深愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷經八千年的時光 只讓這愛意更濃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得別人的事都無關緊要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你相遇以後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識到 人就是想要和他人相連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不要讓生命的流動中斷 柚葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經明白我不是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不是只屬於自己一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只屬於自己一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的生命 超越生與死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 連成一體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔軟的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 屍骸就像在搖籃中…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像兒時被媽媽抱在懷中一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 如果沒有出生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就體會不到這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有出生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能和大家 和Jin相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 洞地外面並不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有著危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:21:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也有著和洞內同樣的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就難免會受傷 承受痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是有唯獨誕生於死亡與再生的縫隙間的樂聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要懼怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠在這裡等著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著大家再次降生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡等著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在流逝的時光中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刻緊接一刻地死亡 一刻緊接一刻地轉生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從無到有的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將名為現在的時刻緊緊相連在心中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念真合體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========ED=========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.68,0:24:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從墓中誕生 居然會變得這麼強大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.00,0:24:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用一直以來的嗶哩嗶哩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.32,0:24:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘎吱嘎吱你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 創聖大天使evol
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛的野獸們
